<H3><A NAME="subj9.1">Re:</A> MCI recommending bad security practices (McDaniel, <A HREF="/Risks/18.06.html">RISKS-18.06</A>)</H3>
<ADDRESS>
Andy Piper
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:andyp@wrath">andyp@wrath</A>&gt;
