<ADDRESS>
Keith Bostic
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:bostic@bsdi.com">bostic@bsdi.com</A>&gt;
</ADDRESS>
<I>Fri, 13 Oct 1995 16:05:02 -0400</I><PRE>

[Appeared in Yucks Digest V6 #7,
from <A HREF="mailto:spaf@cs.purdue.edu">spaf@cs.purdue.edu</A> (Gene "Chief Yuckster" Spafford)]

From: <A HREF="mailto:bzs@world.std.com">bzs@world.std.com</A> (Barry Shein)

So I just get a "spam" complaint from an AOL postmaster threatening:

&gt;From: <A HREF="mailto:Postmaster@aol.com">Postmaster@aol.com</A>
&gt;To: <A HREF="mailto:netadmin@world.std.com">netadmin@world.std.com</A>, <A HREF="mailto:postmaster@world.std.com">postmaster@world.std.com</A>
