"Peter G. Neumann"
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:neumann@csl.sri.com">neumann@csl.sri.com</A>&gt;
</ADDRESS>
<I>Thu, 20 Jun 1996 08:34:39 -0800</I><PRE>

There was a nice article surveying the pachinko bogus-card fiasco noted in
<A HREF="/Risks/18.15.html">RISKS-18.15</A> and 16, and the risks of believing in technological solutions to
not-just-technological problems.

