<A HREF="http://www.cms.dmu.ac.uk/CCSR/ccsr/conf/ethicomp/ethicomp96.html">http://www.cms.dmu.ac.uk/CCSR/ccsr/conf/ethicomp/ethicomp96.html</A>

[Centre for Computing and Social Responsibility, Dept of Computer Science,
De Montfort University, The Gateway, LEICESTER, UK LE1 9BH <A HREF="mailto:ccsr@dmu.ac.uk">ccsr@dmu.ac.uk</A>
