<A NAME="subj1"><IMG SRC="/Images/Lines/hrfadeblue.gif" ALT="---------------------------------------------"></A>
<H3><A NAME="subj1.1">Limits of automated newsgathering</A></H3>
<ADDRESS>
"Terry A. Ward"
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:terrywa@ix.netcom.com">terrywa@ix.netcom.com</A>&gt;
</ADDRESS>
<I>Wed, 4 Dec 1996 11:35:55 -0800</I><PRE>

