Martin Minow
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:minow@apple.com">minow@apple.com</A>&gt;
</ADDRESS>
<I>Fri, 6 Dec 1996 17:15:03 -0800</I><PRE>

&gt;From an article in the Swedish newspaper, Aftonbladet, Dec 6, 1996
written by Claes Thunblad.  <A HREF="http://www.aftonbladed.se/nyheter/dec/06/flyg.html">http://www.aftonbladed.se/nyheter/dec/06/flyg.html</A>

[[Note: while the Swedish translations I send to RISKS are usually from
