<ADDRESS>
Mike Reiter
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:reiter@research.att.com">reiter@research.att.com</A>&gt;
</ADDRESS>
<I>Wed, 11 Dec 1996 17:02:13 -0500 (EST)</I><PRE>

Fourth ACM Conference on Computer and Communications Security
(Preliminary Technical Program, Abridged for RISKS)
Zurich, Switzerland
1-4 April 1997
Sponsored by ACM SIGSAC

For more information, including registration and hotel information,
see: <A HREF="http://www.zurich.ibm.ch/pub/Other/ACMsec/index.html">http://www.zurich.ibm.ch/pub/Other/ACMsec/index.html</A> .

